    <title>litegraph</title>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>A lightweight header only C++ library for graph abstraction and implementation</para><para><heading level="3">Install</heading>
</para><para>Copy paste <computeroutput>inc/litegraph.cpp</computeroutput> to custom project or install to system with <computeroutput>sudo make install</computeroutput></para><para><heading level="3">Test</heading>
</para><para>Compile the <computeroutput>example_test</computeroutput> with <computeroutput>make</computeroutput> and run with <computeroutput>make run</computeroutput>. The example test instantiates and runs routines on the following graph</para><para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">graph<sp/>TD;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">0<sp/>--&gt;1;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">1<sp/>--&gt;2;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">2<sp/>--&gt;3;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">3<sp/>--&gt;1;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">3<sp/>--&gt;3;</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>    </detaileddescription>
